{"tid":2190640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防刀義和團團長#204126 條五毛畜又改名","createTime":"2020-09-05T23:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T20:24:46.000Z","uid":26770,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac8fa693809e1d41efb0bf9f0e528173bdef14c","tid":2190640,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T23:37:21.000Z","msg":"1 )<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1974413/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1974413/page/1</a><br />\n前會員名Power師兄<br />\n自稱19歲開網店ig 賣野，月入8萬,<strong>仲讀過BBA</strong><br />\n<span class=\"red\">幼稚園開始跳級?</span><br />\n<br />\n2) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2172516/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2172516/page/1</a><br />\n以會員名防刀義和團團長開POST<br />\n指控批評警暴者無證據<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但荃灣警局輪姦案,梓樂謀殺案,831明顯見到狗方高層干擾關鍵閉路電視證據?</strong><br />\n<br />\n3)<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/204126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/204126</a><br />\n呢二單野做得太明顯受到大量會員懷疑立即改名狂扮假膠洗底<br />\n現稱 <br />\n拉post_Xander #204126<br />\n-----------------------------------<br />\n<span class=\"red\">現在疫情影響加經濟差, 香港黑社會的雞竇無肉食<br />\n黑社會自鄉黑強成為一哥後條線就更通,於是r埋五毛job<br />\n<br />\n所以點解五毛出自波台,因為公仔佬爛賭</span>"},{"pid":"d3b4ea7960df403e1b534fe84073d0d51bc04b0e","tid":2190640,"uid":26770,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T23:54:16.000Z","msg":"以前就搵北佬,後尾發現用軟件轉走殘體字都穿崩,兩邊表達方法差好遠<br />\n於是轉用廣州狗(中國垃圾公務員,動員大學生,勞改犯)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>最近香港黑道迫害香港異見者有功就成條維穩水分落去</strong><br />\n呢班死仆街撚屌咪就係港奸"},{"pid":"8b4d225f9d76c05f5b1e3004ac2ba4108656ba67","tid":2190640,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"啲老黑識字嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵佢哋搞唔掂架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"